♪My cries♪

180
00:15:08,450 --> 00:15:10,070
♪And sighs♪

181
00:15:10,490 --> 00:15:13,350
♪Are buried in the snow♪

182
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:16,050
♪Horses run♪

183
00:15:16,210 --> 00:15:17,730
♪Into my dreams♪

184
00:15:18,170 --> 00:15:21,480
♪And I see you again♪

185
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:23,750
♪You left♪

186
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:25,590
♪Broke my heart♪

187
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:29,640
♪Wish you could hold me in your arms♪

188
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:32,470
♪Even your name♪

189
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:36,950
♪Is a forbidden word♪

190
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:41,050
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

191
00:15:41,050 --> 00:15:45,300
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

192
