♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

203
00:16:27,470 --> 00:16:31,410
♪Only to call your name again♪

204
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:35,120
♪For it's the only thing♪

205
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:39,420
♪I'll never forget♪

206
00:16:43,290 --> 00:16:46,660
♪Till the day that I die♪
